<L>__{interior student digs. night}
<A>__{michael is working alone at his desk, a light on. the door of his extremely modest student digs is open. marthe appears at the door, silently. he looks up.}
<C>__{marthe}
<D>__{so this is where you are.}
<C>__{michael}
<D>__{yes. come in.}
<A>__{but neither of them move. marthe just smiles from the door.}
<C>__{marthe}
<D>__{you take work seriously.}
<C>__{michael}
<D>__{oh i don't know.}
<C>__{marthe}
<D>__{you're rather a serious boy.}
<A>__{marthe shrugs slightly.}
<C>__{michael}
<D>__{it's how i was brought up. what about you? are you serious?}
<C>__{marthe}
<D>__{you're sure you want to work tonight?}
